From 8f6b58d5dc73e72c7642acd77a498f212cc116ef Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tanzhenyu <tanzhenyu@localhost>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 10:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ui: style text overlays as light acrylic

Use Inter throughout the native text information overlays and replace the
opaque square panels with lightly translucent, cool-grey rounded surfaces.
The gradient, highlight border and fine deterministic grain approximate an
acrylic material while keeping the implementation in niri's existing Cairo
texture path.
---
 src/ui/hotkey_overlay.rs | 112 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 src/ui/mru.rs            | 111 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 2 files changed, 188 insertions(+), 35 deletions(-)

